gomodel:SYNGO_2742  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The authors used an antibody against AP-3 delta for immunofluorescence and immuno EM. The specificity of the antibody was confirmed using an AP-3 delta knockout mouse.\n\nFig.3F: \"AP-3 also labels a dendritic spine in the striatum (F)\"\n\nNote: localization to postsynapse does not represent the majority of AP-3 delta in the synapse (Fig.4).. Experimental description: From the results, \"Using this antibody, we performed immunoperoxidase reactions on Vibratome brain sections from control (WT) and AP-3-deficient Ap3dmh/mh (mocha) mouse brains\"." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7806-5662" ;
        dc:date           "2018-03-01" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2742" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
